					Mandala 1: Hymn 1: Verse 8
				-
					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 1: Verse 8: Line 1
					-
						-
							Ruler of sacrifices, guard of Law eternal, radiant One,
						-
					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 1: Verse 8: Line 2
					-
						-
							Increasing in thine own abode.
