					Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 12
				-
					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 12: Line 1
					-
						-
							Thus, Soma-drinker, may it be; thus, Friend, who wieldest thunder, act
						-
					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 12: Line 2
					-
						-
							To aid each wish as we desire.
