					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 15: Line 2
					-
						-
							Stirrest the axle with thy strength.
						-
				-
					Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 16
				-
					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 16: Line 1
					-
						-
							With champing, neighing loudly-snorting horses Indra hath ever won
							himself great treasures
						-
					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 16: Line 2
					-
						-
							A car of gold hath he whose deeds are wondrous received from us, and
