					Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 18
				-
					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 18: Line 1
					-
						-
							Your chariot yoked for both alike, immortal, ye of mighty acts,
						-
					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 18: Line 2
					-
						-
							Travels, O Asvins, in the sea.
						-
				-
					Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 19
				-
					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 19: Line 1
					-
						-
							High on the forehead of the Bull one chariot wheel ye ever keep,
						-
					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 30: Verse 19: Line 2
					-
						-
							The other round the sky revolves.
						-
