					Mandala 1: Hymn 31: Verse 7
				-
					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 31: Verse 7: Line 1
					-
						-
							For glory, Agni, day by day, thou liftest up the mortal man to highest
							immortality,
						-
					-
						Mandala 1: Hymn 31: Verse 7: Line 2
					-
						-
							Even thou who yearning for both races givest them great bliss, and to
