					Mandala 4: Hymn 14: Verse 1
				-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 14: Verse 1: Line 1
					-
						-
							THE God hath looked, even Agni Jatavedas, to meet the Dawns refulgent
							in their glories.
						-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 14: Verse 1: Line 2
					-
						-
							Come on your chariot, ye who travel widely, come to this sacrifice of
							ours, Nasatyas.
						-
