					Mandala 4: Hymn 14: Verse 2
				-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 14: Verse 2: Line 1
					-
						-
							Producing light for all the world of creatures, God Savitar hath raised
							aloft his banner.
						-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 14: Verse 2: Line 2
					-
						-
							Making his presence known by sunbeams, Surya hath filled the firmament
							and earth and heaven.
						-
