				-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 16: Verse 2: Line 1
					-
						-
							Unyoke, as at thy journey's end, O Hero, to gladden thee today at this
							libation.
						-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 16: Verse 2: Line 2
					-
