					Mandala 4: Hymn 16: Verse 7
				-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 16: Verse 7: Line 1
					-
						-
							He smote away the floods' obstructer, Vrtra; Earth, conscious, lent her
							aid to speed thy thunder.
						-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 16: Verse 7: Line 2
					-
						-
							Thou sentest forth the waters of the ocean, as Lord through power and
							might, O daring Hero.
						-
