					Mandala 4: Hymn 16: Verse 8
				-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 16: Verse 8: Line 1
					-
						-
							When, Much-invoked! the water's rock thou cleftest, Sarama showed
							herself and went before thee.
						-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 16: Verse 8: Line 2
					-
						-
