				-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 16: Verse 13: Line 1
					-
						-
							Thou to the son of Vidathin, Rjisvan, gavest up mighty Mrgaya and
							Pipru.
						-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 16: Verse 13: Line 2
					-
						-
							Thou smotest down the swarthy fifty thousand, and rentest forts as age
