					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 26: Verse 2: Line 2
					-
						-
							I guided forth the loudly-roaring waters, and the Gods moved according
							to my pleasure.
						-
				-
					Mandala 4: Hymn 26: Verse 3
				-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 26: Verse 3: Line 1
					-
						-
							In the wild joy of Soma I demolished Sambara's forts, ninety-and-nine,
							together;
