					Mandala 4: Hymn 26: Verse 4
				-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 26: Verse 4: Line 1
					-
						-
							Before all birds be ranked this Bird, O Maruts; supreme of falcons be
							this fleet-winged Falcon,
