					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 26: Verse 4: Line 2
					-
						-
							Because, strong- pinioned, with no car to bear him, he brought to Manu
							the Godloved oblation.
						-
				-
					Mandala 4: Hymn 26: Verse 5
				-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 26: Verse 5: Line 1
					-
						-
							When the Bird brought it, hence in rapid motion sent on the wide path
							fleet as thought he hurried.
						-
					-
						Mandala 4: Hymn 26: Verse 5: Line 2
					-
						-
