					Mandala 5: Hymn 2: Verse 6
				-
					-
						Mandala 5: Hymn 2: Verse 6: Line 1
					-
						-
							Mid mortal men godless have secreted the King of all who live, home of
							the people.
						-
					-
						Mandala 5: Hymn 2: Verse 6: Line 2
					-
						-
							So may the prayers of Atri give him freedom. Reproached in turn be
							those who now reproach him.
						-
