					Mandala 5: Hymn 2: Verse 9
				-
					-
						Mandala 5: Hymn 2: Verse 9: Line 1
					-
						-
							Agni shines far and wide with lofty splendour, and by his greatness
							makes all things apparent.
						-
					-
						Mandala 5: Hymn 2: Verse 9: Line 2
					-
						-
