					Mandala 5: Hymn 3: Verse 1
				-
					-
						Mandala 5: Hymn 3: Verse 1: Line 1
					-
						-
							THOU at thy birth art Varuna, O Agni; when thou art kindled thou
							becomest Mitra.
						-
					-
						Mandala 5: Hymn 3: Verse 1: Line 2
					-
