							who brings oblation.
						-
				-
					Mandala 5: Hymn 3: Verse 2
				-
					-
						Mandala 5: Hymn 3: Verse 2: Line 1
					-
						-
							Aryaman art thou as regardeth maidens mysterious, is thy name, O
							Self-sustainer.
						-
					-
						Mandala 5: Hymn 3: Verse 2: Line 2
					-
