					Mandala 7: Hymn 56: Verse 25
				-
					-
						Mandala 7: Hymn 56: Verse 25: Line 1
					-
						-
							May Indra, Mitra, Varuna and Agni, Waters, and Plants, and Trees accept
							our praises.
						-
					-
						Mandala 7: Hymn 56: Verse 25: Line 2
					-
						-
							May we find shelter in the Marut's bosom. Preserve us evermore, ye
							Gods, with blessings.
						-
			-
				Mandala 7: Hymn 57
			-
				-
					Mandala 7: Hymn 57: Verse 1
				-
					-
						Mandala 7: Hymn 57: Verse 1: Line 1
					-
						-
							YEA, through the power of your sweet juice, ye Holy! the Marut host is
							glad at sacrifices.
