				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 20: Verse 12: Line 1
					-
						-
							They toil not to defend their bodies from attack, strong Heroes with
							their mighty arms.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 20: Verse 12: Line 2
					-
