					Mandala 8: Hymn 20: Verse 15
				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 20: Verse 15: Line 1
					-
						-
							Blest by your favouring help was he, O Maruts, at the earlier flushings
							of the morn,
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 20: Verse 15: Line 2
					-
						-
							And even now shall he be blest.
						-
				-
					Mandala 8: Hymn 20: Verse 16
				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 20: Verse 16: Line 1
					-
						-
							The strong man to whose sacrifice, O Heroes, ye approach that ye may
							taste thereof,
