					Mandala 8: Hymn 47: Verse 1
				-
					-
						GREAT help ye give the worshipper, Varuna, Mitra, Mighty Ones! No sorrow
						ever reaches him whom ye, Adityas, keep from harm. Yours are incomparable
						aids, and good the succour they afford.
