				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 47: Verse 2: Line 1
					-
						-
							O Gods, Adityas, well ye know the way to keep all woes afar.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 47: Verse 2: Line 2
					-
						-
							As the birds spread their sheltering wings, spread your protection over
							us.
						-
