				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 48: Verse 10: Line 1
					-
						-
							May I be with the Friend whose heart is tender, who, Lord of Bays! when
							quaffed will never harm me-
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 48: Verse 10: Line 2
					-
						-
