				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 85: Verse 13: Line 1
					-
						-
							The Black Drop sank in Amsumati's bosom, advancing with ten thousand
							round about it.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 85: Verse 13: Line 2
					-
						-
							Indra with might longed for it as it panted: the hero-hearted laid
							aside his weapons.
						-
