					Mandala 8: Hymn 85: Verse 18
				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 85: Verse 18: Line 1
					-
						-
							Then wast thou, Chieftain of all living mortals, the very mighty slayer
							of the Vrtras.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 85: Verse 18: Line 2
					-
						-
							Then didst thou set the obstructed rivers flowing, and win the floods
							that were enthralled by Dasas.
