					Mandala 8: Hymn 85: Verse 19
				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 85: Verse 19: Line 1
					-
						-
							Most wise is he, rejoicing in libations, splendid as day, resistless in
							his anger.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 85: Verse 19: Line 2
					-
						-
							He only doth great deeds, the only Hero, sole Vrtra-slayer he, with
