				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 85: Verse 20: Line 1
					-
						-
							Indra is Vrtra's slayer, man's sustainer: he must be called; with fair
							praise let us call him.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 85: Verse 20: Line 2
					-
						-
							Maghavan is our Helper, our Protector, giver of spoil and wealth to
							make us famous.
