							This Indra, Vrtra-slayer, this Rbhuksan, even at his birth, was meet
							for invocation.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 85: Verse 21: Line 2
					-
						-
							Doer of many deeds for man's advantage, like Soma quaffed, for friends
							we must invoke him.
