				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 86: Verse 9: Line 1
					-
						-
							O Caster of the Stone, nor Gods nor mortals have attained to thee.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 86: Verse 9: Line 2
					-
						-
							Thou in thy might surpassest all that hath been made: the Gods have not
