				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 86: Verse 12: Line 1
					-
						-
							Tle holy sages form a ring, looking and singing to the Ram.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 86: Verse 12: Line 2
					-
						-
							Inciters, full of vigour, not to he deceived, are with the chanters,
