					Mandala 8: Hymn 86: Verse 13
				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 86: Verse 13: Line 1
					-
						-
							Loudly I call that Indra, Maghavan the Mighty, who evermore possesses
							power, ever resistless.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 86: Verse 13: Line 2
					-
						-
							Holy, most liberal, may he lead us on to riches, and, Thunder-armed,
