				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 86: Verse 15: Line 1
					-
						-
							May thy truth, Indra, Wondrous Hero be my guard: bear me o'er much woe,
							Thunderer! as over floods.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 86: Verse 15: Line 2
					-
						-
							When, Indra, wilt thou honour us with opulence, all-nourishing and
							much-to-be. desired, O King?
