					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 1: Line 2
					-
						-
							To him who guards the Law, inspired, and fain for praise.
						-
				-
					Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 2
				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 2: Line 1
					-
						-
							Thou, Indra, art the Conqueror: thou gavest splendour to the Sun.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 2: Line 2
					-
						-
							Maker of all things, thou art Mighty and All-God.
						-
				-
					Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 3
				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 3: Line 1
					-
						-
							Radiant with light thou wentest to the sky, the luminous realm of
