					Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 5
				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 5: Line 1
					-
						-
							O truthful Soma-drinker, thou art mightier than both the worlds.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 5: Line 2
					-
						-
							Thou strengthenest him who pours libation, Lord of Heaven.
						-
				-
					Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 6
				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 6: Line 1
					-
						-
							For thou art he, O Indra, wiio stormeth all castles of the foe,
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 6: Line 2
					-
						-
							Slayer of Dasyus, man's Supporter, Lord of Heaven.
						-
				-
					Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 7
				-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 87: Verse 7: Line 1
					-
						-
							Now have we, Indra, Friend of Song, sent our great wishes forth to
