						Mandala 8: Hymn 88: Verse 5: Line 1
					-
						-
							Thou in thy battles, Indra, art subduer of all hostile bands.
						-
					-
						Mandala 8: Hymn 88: Verse 5: Line 2
					-
						-
							Father art thou, aIl-conquering, cancelling the curse, thou victor of
