				-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 83: Verse 4: Line 1
					-
						-
							Gandharva verily protects his dwellingplace; Wondrous, he guards the
							generations of the Gods.
						-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 83: Verse 4: Line 2
					-
						-
							Lord of the snare, he takes the foeman with the snare: those who are
							most devout have gained a share of meath.
						-
