					Mandala 9: Hymn 83: Verse 5
				-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 83: Verse 5: Line 1
					-
						-
							Rich in oblations! robed in cloud, thou corapassest oblation,
							sacrifice, the mighty seat of Gods.
						-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 83: Verse 5: Line 2
					-
						-
							King, on thy chariot-sieve thou goest up to war, and with a thousand
							weapons winnest lofty fame.
