				-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 84: Verse 2: Line 1
					-
						-
							He who hath come anear to creatures that have life, Immortal Soma flows
							onward to all of them.
						-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 84: Verse 2: Line 2
					-
						-
							Effecting, for our aid, both union and release, Indu, like Surya,
