							the songs, who finds the light of heaven.
						-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 84: Verse 5: Line 2
					-
						-
							Winner of wealth, the effectual juice is flowing on, Singer and Sage by
							wisdom, dear as heaven itself.
