					Mandala 9: Hymn 85: Verse 1
				-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 85: Verse 1: Line 1
					-
						-
							FLOW on to Indra, Soma, carefully effused: let sickness stay afar
							together with the fiends.
						-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 85: Verse 1: Line 2
					-
						-
