					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 86: Verse 14: Line 1
					-
						-
							He, clad in mail that reaches heaven, the Holy One, filling the
							firmament stationed amid the worlds,
						-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 86: Verse 14: Line 2
