					Mandala 9: Hymn 86: Verse 15
				-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 86: Verse 15: Line 1
					-
						-
							He who was first of all to penetrate his form bestowed upon his race
							wide shelter and defence.
						-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 86: Verse 15: Line 2
					-
						-
							From that high station which he hath in loftiest heaven he comes
							victorious to all encounters here.
						-
