					Mandala 9: Hymn 86: Verse 19
				-
					-
						Mandala 9: Hymn 86: Verse 19: Line 1
					-
						-
							Far-seeing Soma flows, the Steer, the Lord of hymns, the Furtherer of
							day, of morning, and of heaven.
