				Mandala 10: Hymn 102
			-
				-
					Mandala 10: Hymn 102: Verse 1
				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 102: Verse 1: Line 1
					-
						-
							FOR thee may Indra boldly speed the car that works on either side.
						-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 102: Verse 1: Line 2
					-
						-
							Favour us, Much-invoked! in this most glorious fight against the
							raiders of our wealth.
						-
