				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 102: Verse 4: Line 1
					-
						-
							The bull in joy had drunk a lake of water. His shattering horn
							encountered an opponent.
						-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 102: Verse 4: Line 2
					-
						-
							Swiftly, in vigorous strength, eager for glory, he stretched his
							forefeet, fain to win and triumph.
						-
				-
