				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 102: Verse 5: Line 1
					-
						-
							They came anear the bull; they made him thunder, made him pour rain
							down ere the fight was ended.
						-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 102: Verse 5: Line 2
					-
						-
							And Mudgala thereby won in the contest well-pastured kine in hundreds
