					Mandala 10: Hymn 103: Verse 12
				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 103: Verse 12: Line 1
					-
						-
							Bewildering the senses of our foemen, seize thou their bodies and
							depart, O Apva.
						-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 103: Verse 12: Line 2
					-
						-
							Attack them, set their hearts on fire and burn them: so let our foes
							abide in utter darkness.
						-
