					Mandala 10: Hymn 104: Verse 4
				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 104: Verse 4: Line 1
					-
						-
							O Mighty Indra, through thine aid, thy prowess, obtaining life,
							zealous, and skilled in Order,
						-
