							Lord of the Bays, come with thy two Bay Horses, come to our prayers, to
							drink the juice of Soma.
						-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 104: Verse 6: Line 2
					-
						-
							To thee comes sacrifice which thou acceptest: thou, skilled in holy
							rites, art he who giveth.
						-
