					Mandala 10: Hymn 104: Verse 11
				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 104: Verse 11: Line 1
					-
						-
							Call we on Maghayan, auspicious Indra. best Hero in this fight where
							spoil is gathered,
						-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 104: Verse 11: Line 2
					-
						-
							The Strong, who listens, who gives aid in battles, who slays the
							Vrtras, wins and gathers riches.
