				Mandala 10: Hymn 105
			-
				-
					Mandala 10: Hymn 105: Verse 1
				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 105: Verse 1: Line 1
					-
						-
							WHEN, Vasu, wilt thou love the laud? Now let the channel bring the
