					Mandala 10: Hymn 136: Verse 6
				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 136: Verse 6: Line 1
					-
						-
							Treading the path of sylvan beasts, Gandharvas, and Apsarases,
						-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 136: Verse 6: Line 2
					-
						-
							He with long locks, who knows the wish, is a sweet most delightful
							friend
						-
