					Mandala 10: Hymn 136: Verse 7
				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 136: Verse 7: Line 1
					-
						-
							Vayu hath churned for him: for him he poundeth things most hard to
							bend,
						-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 136: Verse 7: Line 2
					-
						-
							When he with long loose locks hath drunk, with Rudra, water from the
							cup.
						-
