				Mandala 10: Hymn 137
			-
				-
					Mandala 10: Hymn 137: Verse 1
				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 137: Verse 1: Line 1
					-
						-
							YE Gods, raise up once more the man whom ye have humbled and brought
