				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 137: Verse 2: Line 1
					-
						-
							Two several winds are blowing here, from Sindhu, from a distant land.
						-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 137: Verse 2: Line 2
					-
						-
