					Mandala 10: Hymn 138: Verse 6
				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 138: Verse 6: Line 1
					-
						-
							These are thy famous exploits, only thine, when thou alone hast left
							the other reft of sacrifice.
						-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 138: Verse 6: Line 2
					-
						-
							Thou in the heavens hast set the ordering of the Moons: the Father
							bears the felly portioned out by thee.
