				-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 170: Verse 4: Line 1
					-
						-
							Beaming forth splendour with thy light, thou hast attained heaven's
							lustrous realm.
						-
					-
						Mandala 10: Hymn 170: Verse 4: Line 2
					-
						-
							By thee were brought together all existing things, possessor of all
							Godhead, All-effecting God.
						-
